      "text": "Step 18 \n\n构建 MinerU +\nLangExtract +\nLangChain QA的\nAgentic-RAG 的\nMVP 测试链路",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "JCc158vVZ9vJ1JnpdwH4A",
      "originalText": "Step 18 \n\n构建 MinerU + LangExtract + LangChain QA的 Agentic-RAG 的MVP 测试链路",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
